            "html": "<section class=\"section\" id=\"fe-s-clusters\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <h2 class=\"h2\">Fe-S Clusters in Biology</h2>\n    <div class=\"panel pad\">\n      <p class=\"p\">Iron-sulfur clusters are ancient and essential:</p>\n      <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n        <li><strong>Electron carriers</strong> — shuttle electrons in respiration</li>\n        <li><strong>Enzyme cofactors</strong> — enable catalytic function</li>\n        <li><strong>Sensors</strong> — detect oxygen and iron levels</li>\n        <li><strong>Structural elements</strong> — maintain protein shape</li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"p\">Found in: mitochondria, chloroplasts, bacteria, archaea.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
